5A1F4B4A.Line1.6D03F: Both Inarius and Lilith have perished in Hell. I couldn’t begin to guess what that means for Sanctuary.

8E083E4E.Line5.6D03F: Something nasty, knowing our luck. I just hope you’re still with us then.

F413C4CC.Line3.6D03F: There’s no telling what creatures or phenomena might bleed from Hell, closed Gate or no.

FB3FFC35.MenuLabel: “Do you think Sanctuary is safe now?”
